Tuscany Eclipse Plugin Updatesite
=================================

The Tuscany Eclipse plugin helps you simplify your application development usig Tuscany and SCA. 
It provides the following capabilities :

- Define a Tuscany User Library containing all the Tuscany JARs 
  to make it easier to add them to my project buildpath.

- Associate .composite files with the XML editor and register 
  the SCA and Tuscany XML schemas to get code-assist in the editor
  and validation of my composite files.

- Enable right-click on the .composite and select a Run As / Tuscany...
